to create a server(NODE JS, EXPRESS)

1  create a folderand create  package.json -(npm init)
2  create entry point  file : index.js
3  we have to install Express in the server : npm i express
4  import express inside index.js file
5  create server app using express
6  set up port server app
7 to resolve client request
	-HTTP Status code
		1xx-Information
		2xx-Success
		3xx-Redirection
		4xx-
8 To connect  Mongo Db with server -
	8.1 mongoose library - npm i mongoose
9Api call- asynchronous in js - to resolve this we have to use promise.promise has 2 states
	10.1 resolve state- then()
	10.2rejectd state-catch()